\"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 2033, \"end\": 2039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999988407059744, \"rank\": 1.1592952482224872e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1922}, {\"ngram\": \"a low develop\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1944}, {\"ngram\": \"the south\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it set up a very westerly swell to start with, which is not unprecedented, but not typical either.\\\"\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The weather system also drove some interesting local winds.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The weather system\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2163}, {\"ngram\": \"some interesting local winds\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"clocking around and doing all sorts of weird things\\\" due to the mountains and canyons behind the village, he said.\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all sorts\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"weird things\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"the mountains\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2279}, {\"ngram\": \"canyons\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As that storm moved all the way past and the front came through, winds shifted in the west, onshore, it's poured rain ...\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that storm\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"winds\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"the west\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"rain\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It went from as good as it gets to about as bad as it gets in an hour.\\\"\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an hour\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the clock counting down to complete the event, Wallis is in hot demand from surfers, officials and media.\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2628, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the clock counting\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"Wallis\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2576}, {\"ngram\": \"hot demand\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2593}, {\"ngram\": \"surfers\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"media\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My popularity it wanes with how good the waves actually look.\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My popularity\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, yeah, everyone's obviously interested in what the waves were doing over the next few days.\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2712}, {\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2753}, {\"ngram\": \"the next few days\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So Monday's epic conditions maybe made him some friends?\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Monday's epic conditions\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I look back and it wasn't a perfect forecast by any means ... but, yeah, under promise, over deliver.\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2950, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a perfect forecast\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2893}, {\"ngram\": \"any means\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"promise\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"deliver\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2949}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's always a good rule of thumb in forecasting.\\\"\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good rule\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"thumb\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2985}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the verdict for the days ahead?\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3039, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And the verdict\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"the days\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thursday is looking decent with solid, overhead waves but maybe still a little jumbled, then small and, at best, only decent surf for the remainder of the waiting period.\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3210, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"solid, overhead waves\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3093}, {\"ngram\": \"only decent surf\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3169}, {\"ngram\": \"the remainder\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3187}, {\"ngram\": \"the waiting period\", \"from\": 3191, \"to\": 3209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A surfer himself - \\\"that's how I got into this racket\\\" - Wallis said during Tuesday's stormy weather he might go for a quick wave, but at a little river mouth break near the main reef.\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this racket\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3265}, {\"ngram\": \"Wallis\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3275}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday's stormy weather\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3312}, {\"ngram\": \"a quick wave\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3341}, {\"ngram\": \"a little river mouth break\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"the main reef\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ah no ... Well, maybe the river mouth here.\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Well, maybe the river mouth\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But out at Teahupo'o - no way,\\\" he said laughing.\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no way\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's terrifying out there right now.\\\"\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- Reuters Copyright \\u00a92024,Radio New Zealand Tahiti's Teahupo'o stole the show at the Olympic surfing with some of the most incredible waves on Earth.\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"- Reuters Copyright \\u00a9\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3611}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic surfing\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3634}, {\"ngram\": \"the most incredible waves\", \"from\": 3648, \"to\": 3673}, {\"ngram\": \"Earth\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Olympics get going in earnest this week, not everyone's attention is focused on host city Paris.\", \"from\": 3687, \"to\": 3790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3784, \"end\": 3789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.526474259306491e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3702}, {\"ngram\": \"earnest\", \"from\": 3716, \"to\": 3723}, {\"ngram\": \"not everyone's attention\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surf fans are heading to Tahiti, half a world away in French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3816, \"end\": 3822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999988407059744, \"rank\": 1.1592952482224872e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://